Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第八幕\N布洛涅之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.48,0:02:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然進來做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.81,0:02:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.14,0:02:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我怎麼叫你都不回答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香榭麗捨的客人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說今日不想見您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼口信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 沒什麼特別的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:48.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.61,0:02:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望能賞光參觀新別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邀請您參加晚會的請貼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.55,0:02:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請務必與家人同往
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.04,0:02:58.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,榮幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.81,0:02:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:03:02.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奧特伊的森林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.07,0:04:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,Banner;12;0;90,{\a6}{\fs20}Auteuil：巴黎西部市郊的一個區，莫裡哀等作家喜愛居住的地方。周圍是布洛涅（Boulogne）森林。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼荒涼的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 這是伯爵的個人意願
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡…似乎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前是屬於維爾福先生的別墅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.85,0:03:33.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直是廢墟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前的女主人在時 這裡非常華麗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是瓦朗蒂娜的親生母親？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時還是年輕貌美的女士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.71,0:04:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.37,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 是維爾福夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.07,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是外子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首席檢察官大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說內人與犬子承蒙關照
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:40.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得您賞光親臨 實在蓬蓽生輝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這座別墅用來招待客人還稍顯冷清
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 不知為何我特別喜歡清靜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.78,0:05:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 如今代表巴黎的三位紳士都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.39,0:05:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金融王唐格拉爾氏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌攬軍隊實權的莫爾塞夫將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有司掌法律的您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:15.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日招待各位參加這個簡陋的聚會不為別樁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我向大家坦白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.27,0:05:24.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅者是不安之人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望能和三位建立友情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.27,0:05:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍閣下是否渴望大統領的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.40,0:05:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您從何處聽聞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請讓我略盡綿薄之力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 你先離席一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人之間有話要談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.62,0:05:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:06:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 呆坐著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你臉色不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒事 母親
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.04,0:06:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬拉你過來 很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.05,0:06:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵…是不是在避開我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.34,0:06:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在維爾福先生家看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.70,0:06:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…伯爵和夫人有染
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候伯爵發現了我在偷窺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像…是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.17,0:06:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵也有不為人知的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.95,0:07:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是一個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你不是為了馬克西米利安的事而去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是另外一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.90,0:07:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能與二位相伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去吹吹夜風
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在…在下是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克西米利安·莫雷爾大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.19,0:07:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是位傑出的軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下獵犬座γ方面軍陸軍上尉 馬克西米利安·莫雷爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.39,0:07:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本家在馬賽從事貿易 在下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 在下和令嬡…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您從事著保衛國家的高尚工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.48,0:08:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我對表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但您只是一介平民
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而小女已有未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此 望您諒解
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:24.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是越洋而來的馬賽風味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求婚怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…她對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在說什麼悄悄話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博尚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.91,0:08:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然突然對首席檢察官按下快門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夠膽大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.45,0:08:59.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到囂張的傢伙就叛逆心理作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.96,0:09:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 青春的煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.54,0:09:06.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是 這世上一個二個都為情所困
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 以前那兩人也傳過緋聞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首席檢察官和歐仁妮的母親？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.97,0:09:19.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不情之請 實在抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.42,0:09:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 請別介意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:25.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鋼琴課也花了不少錢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.96,0:09:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就得在這種時候露兩手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.56,0:09:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽我說兩句
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想向您道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時我…未考慮您的想法就出言不遜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.33,0:09:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩事都丟給你了 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦朗蒂娜喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.22,0:10:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歐仁妮那傢伙彈得不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被她騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會兒跟她聊過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正又是我說壞話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼呀 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.01,0:10:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今還來找我幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.93,0:10:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看見怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.54,0:10:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我在這裡…把那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂就如您的天職
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天職嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵認識很多有才能的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.32,0:11:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您出色的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美麗的人兒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.90,0:11:45.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為展示年輕人們的才華橫溢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容我再引薦一位年輕人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德烈亞·卡瓦爾坎蒂侯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.45,0:11:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個家族還有繼承人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.43,0:12:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的父親是我的舊友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.08,0:12:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若大家能像待我一樣待他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便不勝榮幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.89,0:12:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是剛繼承亡父領地的後生晚輩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看他的胸飾 看樣子值500萬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.02,0:12:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵的新寵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.83,0:12:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能非常有才華哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.75,0:12:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 抱歉打斷各位暢談
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能承蒙稍微側目一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我買下這座別墅是為了遠離城市喧囂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過清靜離群的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但說來也奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.69,0:12:57.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際來到這裡的我迷上了這幢古宅的某種氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該如何形容呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不禁去想
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從前這座別墅裡人們過著怎樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.74,0:13:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是隱藏了怎樣不為人知的悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次想起 我都充滿著無以言表的喜悅和平穩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.92,0:13:39.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.48,0:13:42.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊 說什麼詛咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.81,0:13:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,檢察官大人察覺不到這座宅子裡陰鬱邪惡的氣氛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.18,0:13:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是首席檢察官
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:14:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 那麼由您親自來確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.51,0:14:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實在這座宅子裡只留有一間未使用的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.21,0:14:09.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那房間被認為是這邪惡氣氛瀰漫的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒謬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了 不要這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.67,0:14:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就遵從一下主人的意願嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.61,0:14:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來參觀一下這間邪惡的房間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.47,0:14:44.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.34,0:14:48.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去的話 也無甚興味
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.76,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有歐仁妮小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.63,0:14:57.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成三組去尋找那間房 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.57,0:15:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓三個年輕人先行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:09.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗宅邸至深之處
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將贈予平安到達的人一份薄禮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.00,0:15:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.29,0:15:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 非常有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.36,0:15:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生 拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.35,0:15:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 侯爵夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.80,0:15:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您氣色不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請認真一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.57,0:15:48.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先發方能制人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順帶一問 侯爵出身何處？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我來自銀河東方的遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一片非常美麗的行星群
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:02.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中某顆星上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.15,0:16:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一種吸取礦石菁華 孕育寶石之卵的鳥類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.32,0:16:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50年1次為繁殖而築巢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:22.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能和您單獨交談了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵 我想和您談談
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:47.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 莫爾塞夫夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我梅爾塞苔絲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪惡氣氛的核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,核心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您為何對馬賽如此介懷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此話怎講
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.28,0:17:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的菜餚也安排了馬賽口味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.64,0:17:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是看到您就想起以前認識的某人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.76,0:17:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長久以來 我都只為再見他一面而活
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在不知為何卻感到恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯爵？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不是孤獨一人 絕不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人一直想念著您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.48,0:17:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要忘了那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.57,0:18:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是亡父給我的護身符
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.47,0:18:08.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望您能收下它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到盡頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適可而止吧 阿爾貝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.89,0:18:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾福先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面有門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:51.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是第一名
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.31,0:18:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否感到愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.96,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對這座別墅奇異的氣氛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.15,0:19:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這宅邸的主人看來不知何為待客之道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請幫我一個小忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.40,0:19:15.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:21.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您如此幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.49,0:19:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見了 在維爾福先生家的溫室
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思 您看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.74,0:19:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人太熱情了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為您一定非常生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 應該由我說對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.46,0:20:09.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也無法與您暢談
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.07,0:20:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我在遠方宇宙得了一種病
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時會不見任何人來修養
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:27.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.10,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.86,0:20:32.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾會感到麻痺而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.27,0:20:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾貝 這是只屬於你和我的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.98,0:20:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於你和我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.80,0:20:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 我會保密的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 拿著這個盒子出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.47,0:20:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…那孩子出生的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子…是那孩子把我們引來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是17年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是伯爵送的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.84,0:21:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.11,0:21:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.50,0:21:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準戀人們的毒針
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而我還不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那毒手也會降臨到自己頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.80,0:21:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一話 巖窟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第九幕\N夢見黑暗之夢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待 然後期待
